NK110(we)003:2690: 'gyur ba ni zag pa'i 'bras bu dang 'khor ba'i
NK110(we)003:2691: mtha' ste 'khor ba nyid ma zad kyi bar la
NK110(we)003:2692: lus kyang de snyed du len pa'o //
NK110(we)003:2693: de ltar shes pa gzu bo lung du ma bstan pas /
NK110(we)003:2694: bag la nyal spyad pa med pa'i yul du chags pas zag pa nyid du byung ba'o //
NK110(we)003:2695: glo bur rkyen gyi zag pa ni /
NK110(we)003:2696: chos nyid zab mo'i don la phyin ci log du rtogs pa'i zag pa dang /
NK110(we)003:2697: grub pa'i mtha' log pa las byung ba'i zag pa dang /
NK110(we)003:2698: rang gi grub pa'i mtha' la zhen yul blo dang bcas pas bzung ba'o //
NK110(we)003:2699: chos nyid zab mo'i don phyin ci log tu rtogs pa ni /
NK110(we)003:2700: rang rig mngon gsum du ma rtogs par yid dpyod
NK110(we)003:2701: tshig gi mtha' la spyod pa'i tha snyad kyi mngon
NK110(we)003:2702: gsum dang rjes dpag la sogs pa'i zag pa /
NK110(we)003:2703: chos nyid mngon gsum la bsgrib pa dang /
NK110(we)003:2704: tshig gi yin tshul blos gzhag pas chos nyid rang
NK110(we)003:2705: snang gi 'gros dang bral nas phyin ci log gi
NK110(we)003:2707: de bzhin stong pa yid kyis gcad pa dang /
NK110(we)003:2708: gsal ba dang rang bzhin med pa yid kyis gcad pa dang /
NK110(we)003:2709: mtha' log nas rgyu 'bras las kyi rgyun gcad pa rnams yin no //
NK110(we)003:2710: grub pa'i mtha' log pa'i zag pa ni /
NK110(we)003:2711: lta ba phyin ci log tu zhugs pa rnams zag pa rang ka mar spyod pa yin la /
NK110(we)003:2712: rang gi grub pa'i mtha' la zhen yul blo dang bcas pa'i zag pa ni /
NK110(we)003:2713: nga'i bla ma las lhag pa med par zhen pa dang /
NK110(we)003:2714: de bzhin du nga'i man ngag las zab pa med do bar zhen pa dang /
NK110(we)003:2717: chos pa nga las ba zang ba med snyam pa'i blo dang ldan pa'i zag pa rnams yin no //
NK110(we)003:2718: zad cing ni gang zad pa dang /
NK110(we)003:2721: gtan tshigs gang gi phyir zad pa dang /
NK110(we)003:2722: dpe gang ltar zad pa dang /
NK110(we)003:2723: zad pa'i dgos pa dang drug gis bstan to //
NK110(we)003:2724: gang la zad na gong ma'i zag pa rnams zad /
NK110(we)003:2725: gang la zad na chos nyid mngon gsum gyi don nyams su myong ba'i skal ldan la zad /
NK110(we)003:2726: gang gis zad na bla ma'i man ngag phyin ci
NK110(we)003:2727: ma log pa dang rang gi brtson 'grus myur bar
NK110(we)003:2728: bstan pas zad / gtan tshigs gang gi phyir zad na /
NK110(we)003:2729: gcig shes kun grol gyi gtan tshigs kyis shes /
NK110(we)003:2730: gcig ma shes pas kun ma shes pa ni /
NK110(we)003:2731: rang gi gnas lugs ma shes pas 'khor 'das kun mi shes la /
NK110(we)003:2732: rang gi rig pa'i gnas lugs phyin ci ma log
NK110(we)003:2733: par shes pas 'khor 'das thams cad kyi mtshan nyid
NK110(we)003:2734: shes pa'o // de'i phyir na bsad pa kun bsad pas sod pa gcig kyang ma sod pa dang /
NK110(we)003:2735: bsad pa gcig bsad pas sod pa kun sod pa'o //
NK110(we)003:2736: chos nyid bya ba tsam du yang blo la grub pa med pas /
NK110(we)003:2737: dngos po'i 'dug tshul rang gis rang zad pa ste /
NK110(we)003:2738: rgyab gcig la rgyab pas phog pa kun la phog pa dang /
NK110(we)003:2739: 'khor ba nyid rang zad pas mya ngan las 'das pa btsal du med pas /
NK110(we)003:2740: rang gnas stong pa nyid du zad pas rkyen gyi blo yod ma myong /
NK110(we)003:2741: de med pas btags pa ming gi mtha' zad pas /
NK110(we)003:2742: tha snyad tshig la ltos mi 'acha'o //
NK110(we)003:2743: de'i phyir na tshig med yi ge las 'das pas brjod pa'i mtha' zad pas /
NK110(we)003:2744: chos las 'das pa'i zad pa zhes bya'o //
NK110(we)003:2745: dpe ji ltar zad na shes bya rang rgyud dag
NK110(we)003:2746: pa mkha' la sprin dengs pa ltar zad pa dang
NK110(we)003:2747: / ngo bo nyid rang dengs pa chu'i snyog ma rang sar dengs pa ltar zad pa dang /
NK110(we)003:2748: 'khrul 'khor gyi rgyun dag pa shing zad me shi ba ltar zad pa dang /
NK110(we)003:2749: chos nyid kyi lam la zad pa lam gyi mthar rang gi them sgor zad pa'o //
NK110(we)003:2750: de ltar zad pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK110(we)003:2751: rgyu zad pas 'khor ba'i 'phreng thag gcad pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK110(we)003:2752: rkyen zad pas mngal gyi grong khyer du mi 'jug pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK110(we)003:2753: rgyu rkyen gnyis ka zad pas 'khor 'das lte chad pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK110(we)003:2754: nyams myong lta bsgom zad pas chos kyi bdag la mi gnas pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK110(we)003:2755: chos zad pas dgrol rgyu med de ye nas grol bar shes pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK110(we)003:2756: 'khrul pa zad pas 'khor ba rgyun chad pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK110(we)003:2757: de ltar zag pa rang zad pa'i chos nyid de la /
NK110(we)003:2758: phra rags dri ma'i rdul med pa ni /
NK110(we)003:2759: phra ba'i rdul dang rags pa'i rdul lo //
NK110(we)003:2760: phra ba la gnyis te 'byung ba phra ba'i rdul
NK110(we)003:2761: phra rab kyi zag pa dang zad pas phung po'i
NK110(we)003:2763: nyon mongs pa'i phra ba'i rdul shes bya'i sgrib pa'i zag pa med pas /
NK110(we)003:2765: rags pa ni 'byung ba'i rags pa shing dang rde'u
NK110(we)003:2766: dang rtsig pa dang snam bu dang bum pa dang
NK110(we)003:2767: / ri dang khang khyim dang ri rab dang gling
NK110(we)003:2768: bzhi'i zag pa zad pas chos kyi bdag ma grub
NK110(we)003:2769: / / nyon mongs pa rags pa 'dod chags zhe
NK110(we)003:2770: sdang gti mug gi zag pa zad pas thob bya
NK110(we)003:2771: don gyi 'bras bu ma grub pas /
NK110(we)003:2772: re dogs gnyis kyi mtha' las 'das te /
NK110(we)003:2773: re gang la yang mi che /
NK110(we)003:2775: 'dod pa gang dang yang bral ba'i /
NK110(we)003:2776: de ltar zag pa de zad pas ni /
NK110(we)003:2778: mnyam pa nyid ces gdags su btub pa yin no //
NK110(we)003:2779: de ma yin na mnyam pa nyid kyi ming gis gdags su mi btub bo //
NK110(we)003:2780: 'o na de gang yin na de lta bu'i mtshan
NK110(we)003:2781: nyid dang ldan pa la chos kyi chos nyid ces
NK110(we)003:2782: pa ste / tha snyad sgros gdags su med pa ni zag pa zag pa'i phyir ro //
NK110(we)003:2783: de ltar zag pa zad pa dang rdul med pa
NK110(we)003:2784: dang chos nyid gsum dbyer med pas mnyam pa chen
NK110(we)003:2785: por thams cad shar zhing gnas pa zhes bya'o //
NK110(we)003:2786: de lta bu'i chos nyid mnyam pa chen po gnyis
NK110(we)003:2787: su med pa'i don de sngon 'byung gi dus su
NK110(we)003:2788: rgyud kyi ston pas gzigs nas gdul bya'i yul la
NK110(we)003:2789: gzigs pa dang / chos nyid rang gi ngo bo la gzigs pa'o //
NK110(we)003:2790: gdul bya ni 'gro ba rang rgyud dag pa gu
NK110(we)003:2791: ru dga' rab rdo rje la sogs pa la gzigs
NK110(we)003:2792: nas gzhan don phyin ci ma log par mthar phyin
NK110(we)003:2794: chos nyid rang gi ngo bo la gzigs stangs gsum
NK110(we)003:2795: gyis gzigs nas ni rang don rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu
NK110(we)003:2796: phyin ci ma log pa mthar phyin par mdzad do
NK110(we)003:2797: // rjes 'jug lam la gnas pa'i skal ldan gyis
NK110(we)003:2798: chos rang gi ngo bo la gzigs stangs gsum gyis
NK110(we)003:2799: // gzigs te / sprul sku'i gzigs stangs kyis bltas pas 'khrul snang sprul pa lta bur mthong la /
NK110(we)003:2800: longs sku'i gzigs stangs kyis bltas pas ye shes sgyu ma lta bur mthong la /
NK110(we)003:2801: chos sku'i gzigs stangs kyis bltas pas chos nyid mtshan
NK110(we)003:2802: nyid bral bar mthong bas rang don phyin ci ma
NK110(we)003:2803: log par rdzogs / de ltar zad pa'i chos nyid
NK110(we)003:2804: mthong bas 'pho ba chen mo'i lus su slar log
NK110(we)003:2805: log par rdzogs / pas / gzhan don phyin ci
NK110(we)003:2806: ma log par mthar phyin pa ni gzigs stangs gsum
NK110(we)003:2807: log par rdzogs / pas / las byung ba'o //
NK110(we)003:2808: de lta bu'i chos nyid la gnas shing phyin ci
NK110(we)003:2809: ma log par mkhyen pa'i ston pa des /
NK110(we)003:2810: 'khor gdul bya rnam par dag pa'i rigs rnams las
NK110(we)003:2811: rdo rje'i ni rigs kyi nang nas yang dag pa'i
NK110(we)003:2812: mkha' 'gro ma ni gsal ba'i yid can ma la
NK110(we)003:2813: / ston pas 'di skad ces tshangs pa'i dbyangs dang ldan pas /
NK110(we)003:2814: tshig 'di ni ston pas sdud pa po mkha' 'gro ma la gsungs so //
NK110(we)003:2815: kye ma nges pa kho nar khyod kyis rna ba'i
NK110(we)003:2816: dbang po sgra gzhan la ma yengs par nyon cig
NK110(we)003:2817: mkha' 'gro ma / nga yis gsang ba'i rgyud gzhung tshig dang yi ger bstan gyis /
NK110(we)003:2818: khyod kyis nga la dang ba'i dad pa dang /
NK110(we)003:2820: yid ches pa'i dad pa dang gsum gyis nyon cig /
NK110(we)003:2821: de ltar khyod kyis lus mi 'gyur bar mdun du drang por 'dug ste /
NK110(we)003:2823: ngag mi 'gyur te brjod pa sgra la ma shor bas dang /
NK110(we)003:2824: yid mi 'gyur te dga' ba dang spro ba'i dad
NK110(we)003:2825: pa dang gsum mi 'gyur ba'i yid kyis yang dag
NK110(we)003:2826: pa'i shes rab phyin ci ma log pas nga'i tshig
NK110(we)003:2827: 'di dag shes rab gsal ba dang /
NK110(we)003:2830: phyin ci ma log pas nyon la /
NK110(we)003:2831: ma 'ongs pa'i dus kyi sems can rnams la khyod
NK110(we)003:2832: kyis rab tu dang pa'i yid kyis gzhan don legs
NK110(we)003:2833: par rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK110(we)003:2834: 'khrul pa med pa'i tshig 'di dag zungs shig ces
NK110(we)003:2835: ston pas gdul bya khyad par can la gzigs nas
NK110(we)003:2836: rgyud kyi rgyal po 'di legs par nyon cig ces
NK110(we)003:2838: da ni spros bcas 'byung ba bzhi'i sgra la sngon
NK110(we)003:2839: du 'gro ba sbyang pa sku gsum gyi sna khrid
NK110(we)003:2841: 'di ltar skyes bu skal ba can //
NK110(we)003:2842: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK110(we)003:2843: tshe 'di la nyams su blangs shing bsgrubs pas 'di
NK110(we)003:2844: ltar rtags dang ldan pa'i skyes bu ni skal pa
NK110(we)003:2845: can zhes bya ba yin no //
NK110(we)003:2846: tshe 'di la chos dang chos nyid gnyis med du rtogs pa de la 'dris par byas pas /
NK110(we)003:2847: de nyid mngon sum du mthong ba don yin /
NK110(we)003:2848: de la goms par byas nas ni /
NK110(we)003:2850: phyir mi ldog pas sngon du nyams len thun mong ma yin pa las byung ba'i /
NK110(we)003:2851: bka' dag pa'i gzhi'i ngo bo mi 'gyur ba /
NK110(we)003:2853: thugs rje khyab pa'i sa la yang dag par gnas pa nyid yin te /
NK110(we)003:2854: de lta bu'i don la skal ba dang ldan pa su yis spyad par nus pa la /
NK110(we)003:2855: lus dang ngag dang sems kyi rtags su yang /
NK110(we)003:2856: rgyud 'di nas bshad pa 'di rnams 'byung ngo mkha' 'gro ma /
NK110(we)003:2858: rten gyi gang zag spros pa la dga' ba gang
NK110(we)003:2859: zhig gis sngon du 'byung ba bzhi'i sa'i sgra don
NK110(we)003:2861: me dang chu dang rlung gi sgra don la goms
NK110(we)003:2862: shing sbyangs pa'i rtags ni goms pa'i tshad der phyin
NK110(we)003:2863: pa dang / 'gro ba rigs drug gi sgra la skal ba dang ldan pa sus goms pa la /
NK110(we)003:2864: tshe 'di la 'byung ba sas mi sub /
NK110(we)003:2867: rlung gis mi khyer bas de dag gis mi gnod cing /
NK110(we)003:2868: lhag par lus kyi yan lag de bzhin du me yis tshig pa med pa ni /
NK110(we)003:2869: shes rab kyis phyi'i sgro 'dogs chod pa'i rtags yin no //
NK110(we)003:2870: lus ni chu yis bying bar mi nus shing zang thal pa ni /
NK110(we)003:2871: chos nyid kyis rang khyab cing sprul pas gzhan don la 'jug pa'i rtags yin /
NK110(we)003:2872: skyes bu 'di yi skra dang gos chu la bor
NK110(we)003:2873: kyang chus 'khyer ba med pas gcig tu sdod pa
NK110(we)003:2874: ni / 'khor bar slar mi ldog pa'i rtags yin /
NK110(we)003:2875: skal ba dang ldan pa de yis rkang pas sa
NK110(we)003:2876: la khru gang gis ma reg par bar snang la
NK110(we)003:2877: 'gro bar nus pa ni sa'i sgra la 'byongs pas
NK110(we)003:2878: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhis sems can gyis don
NK110(we)003:2879: rdzogs par byed pa'i rtags yin /
NK110(we)003:2880: yang skal ldan de 'byung ba rlung gis drang zhing g.yo ba med par /
NK110(we)003:2881: 'di ltar su la byung ba ni /
NK110(we)003:2882: sngon du rlung la 'byongs pas snang ba 'di zad par 'gyur ba'i rtags yin /
NK110(we)003:2883: de ltar 'byung ba'i skal ldan ni /
NK110(we)003:2884: 'byung ba bzhi'i sgra la goms pa'i rtags yin no
NK110(we)003:2885: zhes sku gsum gyi sna khrid pa'i rtags bstan nas
NK110(we)003:2886: / da ni nang don gsum pa sems kyi sna
NK110(we)003:2887: 'a khrid pa'i sngon du 'gro ba 'byongs pa'i rtags
NK110(we)003:2888: / bstan pa ni / sems can snang dang mi snang ba'i //
NK110(we)003:2889: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK110(we)003:2890: sems dri ma tha dad pa'i snang ba can la
NK110(we)003:2891: kun gyis gzhi 'tshogs pa dang bcas par snang dang
NK110(we)003:2892: ni / dbang po lnga'i yul du snang ba'i chos can rnams dang /
NK110(we)003:2893: mi snang ba'i dbang po'i mngon sum du /
NK110(we)003:2894: ma 'dus pa yid kyis bsdus pa'i sems can rnams te /
NK110(we)003:2895: don 'gro ba rigs drug so so'i skad ni skal
NK110(we)003:2896: ba dang ldan pa gang gis shes pa des sngon
NK110(we)003:2897: du sems kyi sngon du 'gro ba la 'byongs pas
NK110(we)003:2898: / da 'gro ba rigs drug gang gi yang gzugs su lus mi len pa'i phyir na /
NK110(we)003:2899: rtags 'di dag rnams ldan pa ni /
NK110(we)003:2900: spyir lus kyi mngon zhen dang /
NK110(we)003:2902: bye brag tu ni 'gro ba mi bsod nams kyis brgyan pa gtso che ba yin no //
NK110(we)003:2903: de nas lha gtso ba dang /
NK110(we)003:2907: dmyal ba dang drug gi skad /
NK110(we)003:2908: mi la gling bzhi las 'dzam bu'i gling gi mi
NK110(we)003:2909: rang la skad rigs mi 'dra ba sum brgya dang
NK110(we)003:2910: drug bcu / shar lus 'phags kyi gling na brgya dang bcu gcig /
NK110(we)003:2911: nub ba lang spyod na skad nyis brgya dang lnga bcu /
NK110(we)003:2912: byang sgra mi snyan na stong dang lnga /
NK110(we)003:2913: lhag ma'i gling bcu drug na /
NK110(we)003:2914: skad rigs mi mthun pa stong bdun brgya dang /
NK110(we)003:2915: 'di ltar gling nyi shu na skad mi 'dra ba
NK110(we)003:2916: sum stong dang bzhi brgya dang nyi shu rtsa drug
NK110(we)003:2917: / gling gzhan dang gzhan gyi skad grangs rnams shes
NK110(we)003:2918: pa ni bsam pa'i shes rab rang rdol ba'i rtags
NK110(we)003:2919: sngon du 'gro ba sems kyi rtags yin no //
NK110(we)003:2920: lha'i skad na 'dod pa la spyod pa'i lha la skad mi 'dra ba drug /
NK110(we)003:2921: gzugs kyi khams la nyi shu /
NK110(we)003:2922: gzugs med pa la bzhi bcu ste /
NK110(we)003:2923: drug bcu rtsa drug shes pa ni /
NK110(we)003:2924: ngag gi sngon du 'gro ba 'byongs pa'i tshad la phebs pa'i rtags yin no //
NK110(we)003:2925: lha min la skad mi 'dra ba bzhi yod de
NK110(we)003:2926: 'di dag rnams shes pa ni ngag gi sgrib pa
NK110(we)003:2928: yang byol song gi skad rigs mi 'dra ba 'bum phrag gnyis dang drug stong lnga brgya yod /
NK110(we)003:2929: 'di dag shes pa ni lus kyi bcings pa las grol ba'i rtags yin no //
NK110(we)003:2930: yi dwags kyi skad brgya nyi shu shes pa ni yid kyi the tshom chod pa'i rtags yin no //
NK110(we)003:2931: dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal nye bar len pa'i skad mi
NK110(we)003:2932: 'dra ba 'bum dang khri phrag gnyis dang nyer lnga
NK110(we)003:2933: dang de dag rnams shes pa ni ngag gi las
NK110(we)003:2934: mthar phyir pa'i rtags yin pas /
NK110(we)003:2935: de dag rnams ci'i phyir shes na skal ldan 'di
NK110(we)003:2936: yis 'gro ba drug gi sems kyi rnam par rtog
NK110(we)003:2937: pa rgyun rang chod pa'i phyir te /
NK110(we)003:2938: de dag rnams su 'jug mi srid pa'i phyir ro //
NK110(we)003:2939: yang 'gro ba drug po'i skad mi 'dra ba de
NK110(we)003:2940: kun gyi sems kyi bsam pa snga phyi ji ltar
NK110(we)003:2941: gyur pa rnams rang gi mngon par shes pas mkhyen
NK110(we)003:2942: pa ni sems las su rung ba'i rtags yin te
NK110(we)003:2943: / de ci'i phyir shes na sems kyi 'khrul pa'i
NK110(we)003:2944: rnam rtog gi bsam pa rnams zad pa'i phyir ro
NK110(we)003:2945: / // de ltar lus ngag yid kyis sngon du 'gro ba tshad du 'byongs pa las /
NK110(we)003:2946: mdor na rna ba'i mngon shes /
NK110(we)003:2950: pha rol gyi sems shes pa dang /
NK110(we)003:2951: dus gsum gcig du shes pa dang /
NK110(we)003:2952: chos nyid zab mo'i don shes pa'i mngon shes dang
NK110(we)003:2953: drug skal ldan de la dus rgyun du 'byung ba
NK110(we)003:2954: ste / 'dis ni 'gro ba drug gi snang ba
NK110(we)003:2955: ma dag pa'i 'di ni sngon du 'gro ba'i skabs
NK110(we)003:2957: de yang gzhan gyis ma yin par rang gis rang
NK110(we)003:2958: bzhin gnas lugs su log nas yang dag pa'i sna
NK110(we)003:2959: 'khrid pas / 'di la mngal gyi grong khyer rgyun
NK110(we)003:2960: gcod pas phyis kyi skye ba'i rgyun bcad pa'i don
NK110(we)003:2961: 'khrid pas / gyi gnad ni / da lta'i tshe
NK110(we)003:2962: 'di las sngon du 'gro ba'i las sbyangs pas snang
NK110(we)003:2963: ba 'di ltar skyes bu 'dis khregs chod du chod
NK110(we)003:2964: 'khrid pas / gyi gnad ni / pas / da lta rang rtags 'di kun 'byung ba'o //
NK110(we)003:2965: zhes sems kyi sna 'khrid par byed pa'i sngon du
NK110(we)003:2966: 'gro ba la 'byongs pa'i rtags dngos gzhi zag pa
NK110(we)003:2967: med pa'i ye shes nyams su longs pa'i dus na
NK110(we)003:2969: da ni rig pa'i sna 'khrid par byed pa 'khor
NK110(we)003:2970: 'das ru shan 'byed pa'i sngon du 'gro ba la
NK110(we)003:2971: lus ngag sbyangs pa'i rtags dngos gzhi'i don rgyud la
NK110(we)003:2972: skyes pa'i dus na 'char bar bstan pa ni /
NK110(we)003:2974: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK110(we)003:2980: ngo bo sdug bsngal bskyed par byed /
NK110(we)003:2981: nges tshig 'khor bas te gcig nas gcig tu 'khor ba'i phyir 'khor ro //
NK110(we)003:2983: ma dag pa'i 'khor ba phyin ci log gis lta bas bsdus pa rnams dang /
NK110(we)003:2984: dag pa phyogs gcig pa'i 'khor ba /
NK110(we)003:2987: yang dag pa'i 'khor ba byang chub sems dpa'i rgyud kyis bsdus pa rnams yin no //
NK110(we)003:2988: 'khor ba'i mtshan nyid ni 'di 'dra ba gcig tu ma nges so //
NK110(we)003:2989: 'bras bu 'gro ba rigs drug dang lam rgyud lngas bsdus pa'i sems can rnams so //
NK110(we)003:2995: myang 'das kyi ngo bo skye shi gnyis las 'das pa'o //
NK110(we)003:2996: nges tshig mya ngan 'chi ba'i dus na sdug bsngal la spyod pa med de /
NK110(we)003:2997: de nyid la 'chi ba med pas mya ngan smre sngags las 'das pas na 'das pa'o //
NK110(we)003:2999: rgyu'i theg pa gsum gyi 'das pa'i sa dang /
NK110(we)003:3000: 'bras bu gsang sngags rnams kyi 'das pa'i sa dang /
NK110(we)003:3001: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i 'das pa'i sa'o //
NK110(we)003:3003: nyan thos kyi 'das pa dgra bcom pa /
NK110(we)003:3004: rang rgyal ba'i ring du song ba rnam pa brgyad /
NK110(we)003:3005: byang chub sems dpa'i bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa'o //
NK110(we)003:3006: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi phyi nang gi mtshan rdzogs rdo rje 'chang gi sa'o //
NK110(we)003:3007: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen pos chos nyid ka nas
NK110(we)003:3008: dag pas spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba
NK110(we)003:3010: mtshan nyid ni rgyu'i theg pa gsum gyi 'das pa'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK110(we)003:3011: sbyang bya gtsor blangs nas rtsol bcas su 'das pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3012: sngags phyi nang gis bsgyur bya gtsor byas nas dbyer med du 'das pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3013: rdzogs pa chen pos mngon gsum gtsor byas nas spang blang rtsol bsgrub med par 'das pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3015: nyan thos kyis skal pa grangs med pa gsum na 'thob la /
NK110(we)003:3016: rang rgyal gyis skal pa grangs med pa gsum na 'thob la /
NK110(we)003:3017: pha rol du phyin pa'i theg pas bskal pa chen
NK110(we)003:3018: po sum cu rtsa gnyis nas 'bras bu thob pa
NK110(we)003:3019: brgyad stong pa'i 'grel pa nas bshad do //
NK110(we)003:3020: sngags phyi nang gis ni phyi pa gsum gyis gos gsum barje ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3021: zas gsum brten pa'i dbang gis tshe gsum nas 'bras bu thob pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3023: don dam pa dang kun rdzob lha dang lha mo'i
NK110(we)003:3024: rang bzhin la brten nas skye ba gcig gis 'bras
NK110(we)003:3026: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen pos ni /
NK110(we)003:3027: gang zag brtson 'grus rab kyis ni zag pa dang
NK110(we)003:3028: bcas pa'i phung po mi snang bar tshe 'di nyid
NK110(we)003:3030: 'bring pos skye ba brgyud pa med par bar ma do la 'bras bu thob pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3031: tha ma yis kyang mngal gyi sgor mi 'grim par
NK110(we)003:3032: rang bzhin sprul pa sku'i zhing khams su bardzusa nas
NK110(we)003:3033: skyes te / de nyid du da bugs byung ste bar ma do med par sangs rgyas thob bo //
NK110(we)003:3034: de ltar 'das pa'i gnas lugs de yang gong ma'i
NK110(we)003:3035: 'khor ba'i chos de dag las sngon du 'gro ba'i
NK110(we)003:3037: ru shan 'byed pa'i spyod pa byas pa las byung ba yin pas /
NK110(we)003:3038: de ltar ru shan phyed pa las /
NK110(we)003:3039: dngos gzhi zag pa med pa'i ye shes nyams su longs pa'i dus na /
NK110(we)003:3040: skyes bu de yi lus ngag yid la rtags 'di rnams 'byung ba yin no //
NK110(we)003:3041: de yang sngon du 'gro ba lus kyi spyod pa
NK110(we)003:3042: byas pas lus 'khor ba las 'jug mi srid pa
NK110(we)003:3043: ni lus rnal du phebs pa'i stobs las byung /
NK110(we)003:3044: ngag gi sngon du 'gro ba'i spyod pa byas pas ngag 'khor ba las 'jug mi srid pa ni /
NK110(we)003:3045: ngag rnal du phebs pa'i stobs la brten nas byung /
NK110(we)003:3046: de bzhin du yid kyi sngon du 'gro ba la goms pa'i rtags 'di dag 'byung ba ni /
NK110(we)003:3047: yid rnal du phebs pa'i stobs la brten nas 'byung pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3048: de la bye brag tu 'di ltar lus kyi sngon
NK110(we)003:3049: 'gro la goms pa'i rtags 'di rnams 'byung ba yin
NK110(we)003:3050: no // rnal 'byor pa de'i lus kyi zhen pa rang log pa'i rtags su /
NK110(we)003:3051: gtan tshigs 'di ltar snang ba'i 'khrul pa ni dngos po las 'khrul pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3053: dngos po las 'khrul pa ni dngos po gshis kyi 'dug tshul las 'khrul pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3055: 'dug tshul ni rtogs te sangs rgyas pa'i snga rol na'ang grub pa'am ming du btags pa med /
NK110(we)003:3056: ma rtogs sems can du grub pa dang ming du
NK110(we)003:3057: btags pa med pa'i sngon rol gyi gzhi de la
NK110(we)003:3060: gzhi dang gzhi shes pa'i khyad par las 'khrul pas /
NK110(we)003:3061: 'khor ba zhes bya bar grub pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3062: de'i rang bzhin las 'khrul pa ni /
NK110(we)003:3063: lhun grub cir yang snang ba las rol pa cir yang shar bas /
NK110(we)003:3064: snang tshul tha dad par byung bas /
NK110(we)003:3065: cir yang nges pa med par 'khrul pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3066: yul las 'khrul pa ni chos nyid kyi bar ma do las 'khrul pas te /
NK110(we)003:3067: gzung ba'i yul las 'khrul pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3069: gzung ba'i yul ni gzung ba'i yul tsam phyin ci log tu rtogs nas 'khrul pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3070: gzung ba'i yul bye brag pa la phyin ci log tu rtogs nas 'khrul pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3071: gzung ba'i yul tsam la phyin ci log tu rtogs pa ni /
NK110(we)003:3072: chos nyid kyi bar ma do la snang ba thams
NK110(we)003:3073: cad kyang 'od dang 'od khyim gyi tshul du shar
NK110(we)003:3074: ba de / rnam par shes pa mngon du rgyu ni lus med pas med do //
NK110(we)003:3075: bag la nyal gyis bzung ste /
NK110(we)003:3076: de ltar snang ba de la shes pa phyin ci log tu gyur pas /
NK110(we)003:3077: 'di ltar snang ba kun la rtog pa btsud pas
NK110(we)003:3078: 'di las nga byung ngam nga las 'di byung snyam
NK110(we)003:3079: pa'i snyam byed las 'khrul pas srid pa bar ma
NK110(we)003:3080: dor las kyi kha brgyud nas 'khor bar 'khrul pa
NK110(we)003:3081: dang / gzung pa'i yul gyi bye brag ni 'od
NK110(we)003:3082: dam thig le'am sku lta bu gcig la yid dpyod
NK110(we)003:3083: kyi shes pa bag la nyal skyes te /
NK110(we)003:3084: phyin ci log tu rtogs te lhag ma rnams kyi rtog pa chod kyang /
NK110(we)003:3085: bye brag pa gcig gis the tshom ma chod pa las 'khor bar 'khrul te /
NK110(we)003:3086: srid pa'i bar ma do la 'khrul pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3087: zhen pa'i yul las 'khrul pa ni /
NK110(we)003:3088: sngar zhen pa'i bag chag gis mtshams sbyor gyi yul las 'khrul pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3089: de nyid glo bur ba'i yul la zhen pa mthar thug dang bcas pas 'khrul ba'o //
NK110(we)003:3090: sngar zhen pa'i yul las phyin ci log tu rtogs nas 'khrul pa ni /
NK110(we)003:3091: 'di'i dus na rmi lam gyi rnam pa dang 'dra ste /
NK110(we)003:3092: da lta'i dus na sngar gyi yul gang dang gang
NK110(we)003:3093: la 'dris pa de mtshan mo'i rmi lam gyi dus
NK110(we)003:3095: 'di'i dus na sngar gyi bag chags bzang ngan gang
NK110(we)003:3096: bsags pa rnams kyis zhen pa snang ba yin pas
NK110(we)003:3097: / 'di'i dus kyi ye shes lnga yi snang ba 'di dag la yang /
NK110(we)003:3098: sngar gyi bag chags kyi stobs kyis skabs su rang
NK110(we)003:3099: gi sngar zhen pa'i bag chags su gyur bas te
NK110(we)003:3101: de'i dbang gis bag chags kyi stobs kyis de nyid
NK110(we)003:3102: la phyin ci log tu rtogs pas srid pa'i bar
NK110(we)003:3104: de nyid las bzang ngan gyi dbang gis 'gro ba drug tu 'khrul pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3105: zhen yul glo bur ba las 'khrul pa ni /
NK110(we)003:3106: 'di'i dus kyi ye shes lnga'i snang ba 'di la gces pa'am sdug par bzung bas /
NK110(we)003:3107: de nyid zhen pa mthar thug pa dang bcas pa'i
NK110(we)003:3108: dbang gis srid pa'i bar ma do la 'khor ba'i
NK110(we)003:3110: de dag gi zhen pa'i rgyun gcad pa ni /
NK110(we)003:3111: dngos po las 'khrul pa la 'khrul gzhi rtsis kyi yi ges gcad /
NK110(we)003:3112: gzung pa yul la 'khrul pa'i rgyun rten 'brel thabs kyi ngo sprod kyi gcad /
NK110(we)003:3113: zhen pa'i yul las 'khrul pa'i rgyun goms pa'i gnad kyi ngo sprod kyis gcad pa'i phyir ro //
NK110(we)003:3114: de ltar chod pa'i rtags su yo gi ni rang
NK110(we)003:3115: gi lus la chags pa med par sems can lus
NK110(we)003:3116: su 'dod pa la gtong bar nus pa ste /
NK110(we)003:3117: dper na rgyal po zla bas /
NK110(we)003:3118: lus kyi mgo brgya rtsa brgyad gtong bar dam bcas nas gtong pa dang 'dra /
NK110(we)003:3119: de'i phyir na mgo dang rkang lag gtong zhing zhum pa'i sems kyang med zhes pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3120: chos nyid stong pa nyid kyi don khong du chud pa'i rtags su /
NK110(we)003:3121: phyi rol gyi rgyan nam mkha' la yo gi 'di ni bskyod pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3123: thogs pa med par rgyu ba'i phyir /
NK110(we)003:3124: rnal 'byor nam mkha'i bya lam gnas zhes pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3125: de bzhin du rig pa dngos med zang thal du rtogs pa'i rtags su /
NK110(we)003:3126: yo gi de'i rags pa kun rten gyis 'di la 'dzul bar nus pas te /
NK110(we)003:3127: stong phrag brgya pa las kyang /
NK110(we)003:3128: sa la yang bya bzhin zhes pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3129: rnal 'byor pa 'dis sems kyi rnam par rtog pa rgyun chad pa'i rtags su /
NK110(we)003:3130: sems can rnams kyi bsam pa yo gi 'dis shes pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3131: 'du shes kun gyi don shes shing zhes pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3132: de bzhin du 'khor ba'i chos rnams kyi mtshan nyid shes pa'i rtags su /
NK110(we)003:3133: mi bsam pa ni bem po'i snang ba rnams kyi don yo gi 'dis shes pa ste /
NK110(we)003:3134: 'khrul snang chen po'i bem rig 'byed pa'i rgyud las /
NK110(we)003:3135: bem po rnams la ci dgar rol zhes pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3136: bsgom pa las byung ba'i shes rab rang rdol ba'i rtags su /
NK110(we)003:3137: kha nas tshig rgyud rim par spros pa'i chos sngar
NK110(we)003:3138: thos ma myong pa'i gzhung tshig dang yi ger bkod
NK110(we)003:3139: pa rnams / sngon chad yongs su grags pa'i 'dod pa'i srol dang mthun par shes pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3140: mi mthun pa'i rim pa spang shes shing /
NK110(we)003:3141: yo gi de'i kha nas kyang smra bar 'byung ba ste /
NK110(we)003:3142: yul mu stegs can rnams tshar gcod nus pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3143: 'di ltar rnal 'byor pa su la byung ba'i mi de ni /
NK110(we)003:3144: sngon du 'gro ba la goms pa'i rtags yin pa'i phyir na /
NK110(we)003:3145: smra ba'i dam pa mchog gi gnas zhes pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3146: rtags de dag rnams dang ldan pa'i skal ldan ni /
NK110(we)003:3147: lus dang ngag dang sems kyis 'di ni 'khor ba'i
NK110(we)003:3148: 'ching ba'i rnam par rtog pa'i zhen pa gang gis
NK110(we)003:3149: ni gong ma 'khrul pa gnyis po'i bcings pa kun
NK110(we)003:3150: las yang dag par grol ba ste /
NK110(we)003:3151: skyes bu 'dis phyis 'khor ba'i lus ngag sems kyi 'brel pa chod par nges pa ste /
NK110(we)003:3152: de ni sngon du ru shan phyed pa las byung
NK110(we)003:3153: ba'o zhes rig pa'i sna 'khrid pa'i sngon 'gro las
NK110(we)003:3155: de dag dril nas sngon du 'gro ba'i rtags bstan nas /
NK110(we)003:3156: da ni dngos gzhi zag pa med pa'i ye shes
NK110(we)003:3157: kyi don nyams su blangs pa las byung ba'i rtags
NK110(we)003:3158: ston te / 'di la bcus bstan pa'i dang po
NK110(we)003:3159: lta ba'i don rtogs shing khong du chud pa'i rtags
NK110(we)003:3160: ston te / bstan pa ni / lta ba la ni goms pa'i rtags //
NK110(we)003:3161: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan /
NK110(we)003:3162: lta ba ni ngo bo dang /
NK110(we)003:3167: lta ba'i ngo bo ni mthong ba yin la /
NK110(we)003:3168: nges tshig ni gang la lta ba'i yul de phyin
NK110(we)003:3169: ci ma log pa mthong ba'i don myong ba rgyud
NK110(we)003:3171: dbye na 'jig rten pa'i lta ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3172: 'jig rten pa ma yin pa'i lta ba'o //
NK110(we)003:3173: 'jig rten pa ni btags pa'i lta ba ming du grags pa rnams yin la /
NK110(we)003:3174: phyin ci log gi lta ba mu stegs rtag chad /
NK110(we)003:3175: ma dag pa'i lta ba nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas /
NK110(we)003:3176: dag pa phyogs ma mthong ba'i lta ba pha rol du phyin pa dang sngags phyi nang ngo //
NK110(we)003:3177: 'jig rten pa'i lta bar 'jog pa ni 'di dag
NK110(we)003:3178: rnams kyis chos nyid mngon sum gyi don mthong ba
NK110(we)003:3179: med pas so so'i skye bo dang khyad par cung
NK110(we)003:3181: 'jig rten par bzhag ste 'jig rten las mi grol ba'i phyir ro //
NK110(we)003:3182: 'jig rten pa ma yin pa'i lta ba la gsum ste /
NK110(we)003:3183: chos can lta ba'i khyad par du /
NK110(we)003:3184: a nu man chod kyi yo ga gsum ste /
NK110(we)003:3185: phyi chos can gyi snang ba la ltas pas na /
NK110(we)003:3186: chos can gyi don mthong ma myong bas 'jig rten pa dang mthun /
NK110(we)003:3187: chos nyid lta ba'i lta ba rdzogs pa chen po
NK110(we)003:3188: sems kyi sde dang klong gi sde dang man ngag
NK110(we)003:3189: gi sde kha cig yin te /
NK110(we)003:3190: chos nyid 'ba' zhig la bltas pas /
NK110(we)003:3191: chos thams cad gnas lugs yin thog tu lus pas /
NK110(we)003:3192: rang gi rig pa la mngon gsum du nyams su myong ba ma skyes pas /
NK110(we)003:3193: gzhan rgyud shes bya'i chos nyid gtan la phebs kyang
NK110(we)003:3194: rang rgyud rnam par grol ba'i ye shes rang gi
NK110(we)003:3195: ngo bo'i mtshan nyid ma mthong bas /
NK110(we)003:3196: 'di nyid la sangs mi rgya bas yang dag pa'i lta ba ma yin /
NK110(we)003:3197: rang rig lta ba'i lta ba ni rdzogs pa chen po 'di'i lugs yin te /
NK110(we)003:3198: rang gi rig pa dbang po'i mngon gsum du gtan la phab nas /
NK110(we)003:3199: don nyams su myong ba rang rgyud la da lta
NK110(we)003:3200: skyes pas phung po'i zag pa 'di nyid la zad
NK110(we)003:3201: nas rdos bcas mi snang ba'o //
NK110(we)003:3202: lta ba rang gi mtshan nyid ni /
NK110(we)003:3203: gang la lta na so so'i yul mtshan nyid ma 'khrul ba la blta /
NK110(we)003:3204: gang gis lta na tshig gi yul sgros tha snyad sna tshogs pa'i yul la /
NK110(we)003:3205: shes rab phyin ci ma log pas blta /
NK110(we)003:3206: rang rig mngon gsum gyi 'khrul pa med pa la /
NK110(we)003:3207: mig gi dbang po'i de nyid ma 'khrul bas blta /
NK110(we)003:3208: chos can sna tshogs pa'i mtshan nyid kyi yul la /
NK110(we)003:3209: thabs dang 'jug sgo khyad par can gyis nyams su myong bas blta ba'o //
NK110(we)003:3210: ji ltar lta na phyin ci log gi blo dang bral bas lta'o //
NK110(we)003:3211: de ltar bltas pas gang mthong na so so'i mtshan nyid phyin ci ma log par mthong ba'o //
NK110(we)003:3212: de ltar mthong ba'i 'bras bu ni 'jig rten pa'i
NK110(we)003:3213: lta ba'i 'bras bus 'jig rten mthun snang du grub
NK110(we)003:3214: la / 'jig rten pa ma yin pa'i lta ba'i
NK110(we)003:3215: 'bras bu ni chos can chos nyid du 'gyur ba
NK110(we)003:3216: la / dang / chos nyid gang gi ngo bor yang ma grub pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3217: rang rig tshegs med du sangs rgya ba nyid du 'gyur ro //
NK110(we)003:3218: de yang 'dir ni lta ba de dag gi nang
NK110(we)003:3219: nas rang rig lta ba'i lta ba la rnal 'byor
NK110(we)003:3221: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po 'di nyid kyi skal pa dang ldan pa'i skyes pa'am bud med la /
NK110(we)003:3222: rtags 'di bzhin du yang da lta'i lus ngag sems la 'byung bar 'gyur ba yin te /
NK110(we)003:3223: de yang chos nyid stong pa rnal 'byor pa de'i
NK110(we)003:3224: lus dang sems la gang zhing rgyas pa'i rtags su
NK110(we)003:3225: mkha' la 'gro ba'i bya bzhin te nam mkha' 'di
NK110(we)003:3226: la thogs pa med par rgyu ba ni lta ba
NK110(we)003:3227: chos nyid du rtogs pa las byung ba ste /
NK110(we)003:3228: de'i phyir na pha rol du phyin pa nas /
NK110(we)003:3229: nam mkha' gnas te cig char cho 'phrul rnam par ston /
NK110(we)003:3231: yang skal pa dang ldan pa'i skyes bu des rlung
NK110(we)003:3232: la brten pa'i lta ba'i don phyin ci ma log
NK110(we)003:3233: par rtogs pas / nang lus kyi rlung la rnal
NK110(we)003:3234: 'byor pa de rang gis sngon du spros bcas dang
NK110(we)003:3235: par rtogs pas / spros med dang / shin tu spros pa med pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3236: rab tu spros pa med pa'i dbang bzhi rdzogs par byas pas /
NK110(we)003:3237: tha ma de nyid la dbang thob pas phyi nang gi snang ba rnams la /
NK110(we)003:3238: goms pa'i stobs kyis gang ltar ci yang bsgyur ba'i /
NK110(we)003:3239: rdzu 'phrul dang stobs rdzogs pa'i phyir na /
NK110(we)003:3240: dper na bar snang la rgyu ba'i phyi'i rlung bzhin du skad cig ma drug brgya'i bar du /
NK110(we)003:3241: rnal 'byor pa 'di yis lus kyi rdzu 'phrul la
NK110(we)003:3242: brten nas 'dzam bu'i gling du rgyu zhing dge ba
NK110(we)003:3243: dang mi dge ba'i mtshan nyid shes shing /
NK110(we)003:3244: de nyid kyi bar la don bya ba dang mi
NK110(we)003:3245: bya ba'i nus pa dang ldan par 'gyur ba yin
NK110(we)003:3246: no // de'i phyir na skad cig thams cad bye brag phyed ces pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3247: yang lta ba'i don rang gi sems nyid stong par rtogs pa'i rtags su /
NK110(we)003:3248: phyi rol gyi bem po'i rnam pa'i ri dang mkhar
NK110(we)003:3249: khyim la sogs pa dngos po'i rnam pa gang la
NK110(we)003:3250: mig gis bltas pa tsam gyis dngos po med pa
NK110(we)003:3251: lhan lhan zhu bar nus pa 'dis ni /
NK110(we)003:3252: rang gi sems kyi mtshan nyid stong pa nyid du rtogs pas te /
NK110(we)003:3253: dngos po'i dmigs rten zhu bar 'gyur zhes skal pa gcod pa'i 'khor lo las so //
NK110(we)003:3254: de lta bu'i rtags rdzogs par byung ba'i rnal 'byor
NK110(we)003:3255: pa 'dis ni lta ba'i gdeng rnyed pa yin no
NK110(we)003:3256: // zhes lta ba rtogs pa'i rtags bstan nas /
NK110(we)003:3257: da ni bsgom pa goms shing 'dris pa'i rtags rnal
NK110(we)003:3258: 'byor pa'i lus ngag la ji ltar 'byung ba bstan
NK110(we)003:3259: pa ni / gang gis sgom la 'byong ba'i rtags /
NK110(we)003:3260: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK110(we)003:3261: gang gis ni rnal 'byor pa gang zhig gis /
NK110(we)003:3262: sgom la ni ngo bo dang /
NK110(we)003:3265: sgom pa rang gi mtshan nyid dang /
NK110(we)003:3267: sgom pa'i ngo bo ni thob bya'i don de dang mi 'bral ba yin la /
NK110(we)003:3268: nges tshig ni gang thob par byed pa'i don de
NK110(we)003:3269: mi gtong zhing yun ring por gnas par byed pa'o
NK110(we)003:3270: // dbye ba ni ming gi sgom pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3271: 'jig rten blo snang 'khrid pa'i sgom pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3272: mtshan ma dmigs gtad kyi sgom pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3273: rtsa rlung ngal so'i sgom pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3274: chos nyid rang thog tu gnas pa'i sgom pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3275: rang bzhin ma bcos pa'i sgom pa dang lnga'o //
NK110(we)003:3276: ming ni ming du btags pa rnams so //
NK110(we)003:3277: 'jig rten pa'i blo sna khrid pa'i /
NK110(we)003:3279: mi bde ba'i skyon 'chos pa'i sgom pa rnams yin no //
NK110(we)003:3280: mtshan ma dmigs gtad dang bcas pa'i sgom pa ni /
NK110(we)003:3281: bskyed pa'i rim pa gtsor bsgom pa dang thabs mi 'dra ba gtsor sgom pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3282: rtsa rlung ngal gso'i sgom pa ni sgom gyi lam stegs su 'gro ba yin no //
NK110(we)003:3283: chos nyid rang thog na gnas pa'i sgom pa ni /
NK110(we)003:3284: gnas dang rten pa'i lam du byed pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3285: rang bzhin ma bcos pa'i sgom pa ni /
NK110(we)003:3286: byas bcos dang 'bad rtsol med par thams cad rang sar bzhag ste /
NK110(we)003:3287: 'di la rtsol ba med pas byas pa'i phyogs su
NK110(we)003:3288: ma lhung ste blo sna khrid pa'i sgom pa'i skyon
NK110(we)003:3289: med / yid kyi yul du mi sgom pas mtshan
NK110(we)003:3290: ma dmigs gtad dang bcas pa'i sgom pa'i skyon med
NK110(we)003:3291: med / / lus ngag yid kyi gcun pa la
NK110(we)003:3292: mi ltos pas rtsa rlung sems kyi ngal gso'i sgom
NK110(we)003:3293: med / / pa'i skyon min / gnas pa tshan
NK110(we)003:3294: che ba'i zhi gnas phyogs gcig tu ma lhung bas
NK110(we)003:3295: med / / pa'i skyon min / / chos nyid
NK110(we)003:3296: rang thog tu gnas pa'i bsgom pa'i skyon med pas
NK110(we)003:3297: med / / pa'i skyon min / / / tshogs drug rang yan /
NK110(we)003:3299: snang ba gcer bzhag tu gzhag pas /
NK110(we)003:3300: rang bzhin gnas lugs kyi bsgom pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3301: mtshan nyid ni gang sgom na chos nyid dngos po'i
NK110(we)003:3302: 'dug tshul gyi mtshan nyid phyin ci ma log par
NK110(we)003:3303: sgom / gang gis sgom na rnal 'byor pa mtshan
NK110(we)003:3304: nyid dang ldan pa 'khor ba las yid dbyung ba
NK110(we)003:3305: sgom / gcig gis sgom / sgom lugs ji ltar sgom na /
NK110(we)003:3306: ma bcos rang bzhag chen por sgom pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3307: 'bras bu ni blo'i babs spyod pa'i 'bras bu dang /
NK110(we)003:3308: mthar thug rang grol gyi 'bras bu'o //
NK110(we)003:3310: dang po so ma zhes pa rang ngo yin snyam pa tsam 'bras bur snang ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3311: gnyis pa lus ngag gi bde ba skyes pa 'bras bur snang ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3312: gsum pa gnyug ma stong pa'i don go ba tsam 'bras bur gyur pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3313: bzhi pa ma bcos pa lus ngag gnad la mi ltos pa 'bras bur 'dod pa ste /
NK110(we)003:3314: 'di dag ni shes pa blo'i yid kyi phyogs mtshon pa yin no //
NK110(we)003:3315: mthar phyin rang grol gyi 'bras bu sku gsum du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa dang bral nas /
NK110(we)003:3316: chos thams cad zad pa nyid la gnas pa yin no //
NK110(we)003:3317: de ltar rang bzhin ma bcos pa'i sgom pa'i don la 'byongs pa'i rtags bstan pa ni /
NK110(we)003:3318: chos nyid skye ba med pa'i don la sgom pas goms pa sngon du gyur pa'i rtags su /
NK110(we)003:3319: rnal 'byor pa de'i lus la 'bu dang srin bu
NK110(we)003:3320: dang srog chags shig dang sro ma la sogs pa
NK110(we)003:3321: med pa ni / sems can thams cad kyang skye ba med par 'khor ba las sgrol ba yis /
NK110(we)003:3322: sems can la dmigs pa'i snying rje dang /
NK110(we)003:3323: bdag gis chos zab mo'i don rtogs par byas pas /
NK110(we)003:3324: gzhan don rdzogs par bya'o snyam pa'i blo 'byongs pas
NK110(we)003:3325: chos nyid la dmigs pa'i snying rje sems can gyi
NK110(we)003:3326: gzhan don dang / rang gi don gnyis mthar phyin par bya ba'i phyir na /
NK110(we)003:3327: rang gi lus la srog chags 'byung mi srid pa ni /
NK110(we)003:3328: kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems 'byongs pa'i rtags yin no //
NK110(we)003:3329: yang skal ba dang ldan pa des /
NK110(we)003:3330: rnam pa yul la brten par rtogs pa de nyid
NK110(we)003:3331: blo du mas spyad pa 'khrul pa'i sems dang phyin
NK110(we)003:3334: byang chub kyi sems don dam dang /
NK110(we)003:3336: kun rdzob gyi rnam pa rgyun skye bar byed pa'i sems stong pas /
NK110(we)003:3337: da sems kyi byung tshor mi 'byung ba'i rtags su /
NK110(we)003:3338: skal ldan de'i lus ni shing bal gyi 'dab ma g.yengs su gnas pa'am /
NK110(we)003:3339: bya sgro'i rnam pa lta bu'am /
NK110(we)003:3340: ras bal bzhin rab tu yang par 'gyur ba yin no //
NK110(we)003:3341: yang rten gyi gang zag gis rang gi rig pa de nyid sngar ma skyes pa'i don dang /
NK110(we)003:3342: da 'chi ba med pa'i don khong du chud cing
NK110(we)003:3343: rtogs pa dang ldan pa'i rang gi don rtogs pa'i
NK110(we)003:3344: rtags su / de'i lus ni lo bcu drug lon pa bzhin du 'gyur ba'o //
NK110(we)003:3345: yang gang zag de nyid la chos nyid stong pa
NK110(we)003:3346: nyid kyi rlan gyis rang gi sems nyid la khyab
NK110(we)003:3347: pa'i phyir na / gang zag de'i lus kyi ba spu dang /
NK110(we)003:3349: lus spyi'i sha mdog la sogs pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3350: de bzhin du so dang sen mo dang skra rnams
NK110(we)003:3351: la rang bzhin gyis snum ma byugs par bag la
NK110(we)003:3353: snum lcug dang ldan pa ni /
NK110(we)003:3354: de ni chos nyid stong pa nyid kyi sgom pa tshad 'byongs pa'i rtags so //
NK110(we)003:3355: yang skal ba dang ldan pa'i gang zag gcig la
NK110(we)003:3356: sems kyi sgom pa mngon du gyur pa'i rtags ni
NK110(we)003:3357: / 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad la /
NK110(we)003:3358: rnal 'byor pa de'i sems ni skad cig kyang snang ba'i rkyen ji ltar byung yang /
NK110(we)003:3359: sa gcig tu gnas pa las gang la yang mi 'phro bar /
NK110(we)003:3360: thog ma gang du gtad pa'am bar snang gi sar sdod cing /
NK110(we)003:3361: 'khrul pa'i yul gnyis ma rig pa nyid 'jug par mi nus par rang sar gnas shing /
NK110(we)003:3362: rnam rtog gi dbang du mi 'gro ba ni nang gi rtags te /
NK110(we)003:3363: rtags 'dis ni bsgom pa gzhan ma yin pa rang gis rnyed pa yin pas na /
NK110(we)003:3364: 'di dag ni sgom pa 'byongs pa ste /
NK110(we)003:3365: 'di dag rnams dang ldan pa'i skal ldan ni /
NK110(we)003:3366: tshe 'di dang gnyis kyis ni rtogs pa mngon du gyur pa'i sangs rgyas thob par nges so //
NK110(we)003:3367: zhes sgom pa las byung ba'i rtags bstan nas /
NK110(we)003:3368: da ni chos nyid kyi yul 'od la goms pa'i rtags bstan pa ni /
NK110(we)003:3369: gang gis 'od la sus goms pa //
NK110(we)003:3370: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK110(we)003:3378: 'od kyi ngo bo ni rang gi gdangs ston par byed pa nyid yin la /
NK110(we)003:3379: nges tshig ni yul rnam par dag pa la snang bar byed pa'i phyir na 'od /
NK110(we)003:3380: rang gi rang bzhin ston par byed pa'i phyir na 'od /
NK110(we)003:3381: thugs rje rang shugs kyis ston pas na 'od do //
NK110(we)003:3384: ye shes lnga'i rang gi mtshan nyid kyi 'od dang /
NK110(we)003:3385: bsod nams lus stobs kyi 'od dang /
NK110(we)003:3386: nyams blangs goms tshad kyi 'od do //
NK110(we)003:3387: ming ni ming du btags pa rnams yin la /
NK110(we)003:3394: srin bu me khyer kyi 'od dang /
NK110(we)003:3395: yi dwags kyi 'od la sogs pa ste 'di dag
NK110(we)003:3396: rnams 'od yin yang mtshan nyid dang mi ldan pa'o
NK110(we)003:3397: // bsod nams lus stobs kyi 'od ni /
NK110(we)003:3400: 'jig rten pa ni gzugs kyi khams kyi lha rnams
NK110(we)003:3401: la bsod nams las grub pa'i 'od la re bas
NK110(we)003:3403: 'das pa ni nyan thos kyi 'od dang /
NK110(we)003:3406: sangs rgyas kyi gzugs sku gnyis kyi 'od do //
NK110(we)003:3407: ye shes lnga'i rang gi mtshan nyid kyi 'od ni /
NK110(we)003:3408: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes rang gi mtshan nyid
NK110(we)003:3409: la 'od mthing ka chos nyid lam gyi rang gdangs
NK110(we)003:3410: su gnas pas / lta ba rang gi ngo bo las mi 'gyur bar snang bar byed la /
NK110(we)003:3411: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi 'od dkar po chos nyid lam gyi zer gdangs su snang bas /
NK110(we)003:3412: sgom pa rang gnas pa'i gshis snang bar byed /
NK110(we)003:3413: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes rang gi mtshan nyid
NK110(we)003:3414: 'od ser po chos nyid lam gyi gting gdangs su
NK110(we)003:3415: snang bas / spyod pa rang gi yon tan du snang bar byed /
NK110(we)003:3416: so sor rtog pa'i 'od dmar po chos nyid lam gyi khyab pa'i ye gdangs su gnas pas /
NK110(we)003:3417: 'bras bu rang dbang ba'i rtsal snang bar byed /
NK110(we)003:3418: bya ba grub pa'i rang gi mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i
NK110(we)003:3419: 'od ljang gu chos nyid rtsal gdangs su snang bas
NK110(we)003:3420: / rig pa rang gi ngo bo rtsol sgrub dang bral bar snang bar byed pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3421: nyams su blangs pa goms tshad kyi 'od ni /
NK110(we)003:3422: rten gyi gang zag gcig gis nyams su blangs pa'i tshe /
NK110(we)003:3423: nyams gong nas gong du 'phel ba'i snang ba kha
NK110(we)003:3424: dog dang dbyibs mi 'dra ba tha dad par snang
NK110(we)003:3425: ba ste / 'od kyi dum bu dang /
NK110(we)003:3430: rin po che'i d+r+wa ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3435: mig mngas ris la sogs pa nang gi rtags kyi skabs nas ston pa yin no //
NK110(we)003:3436: 'od de dag ni dngos po'i gshis la cha tshang
NK110(we)003:3437: ba grub pa rang gi cha tsam du yod pa
NK110(we)003:3438: las / phyi rol snang byed du yod pa ma yin te /
NK110(we)003:3439: dper na til 'bru la mar gyis khyab pa dang mtshungs so //
NK110(we)003:3440: 'di dag ni lam gyi snang cha'o //
NK110(we)003:3441: yang dag pa'i chos nyid zab mo'i ngo gang la
NK110(we)003:3442: 'od yod ces pa'am med bya ba gang yang grub
NK110(we)003:3443: pa med do // 'di ni tshig gis brjod par daka'o //
NK110(we)003:3444: mtshan nyid ni gsal byed gzhan la ma ltos pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3445: de yang gsal bya rang gi rang bzhin de gsal byed du nyams su myong ba las /
NK110(we)003:3446: myong gsal gnyis su med par gsal ba'o //
NK110(we)003:3447: 'bras bu ni chos kyi dbyings bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ngang du sangs rgya'o //
NK110(we)003:3448: de lta bu'i 'od kyi lam snang la skyes bu sus goms pa ni /
NK110(we)003:3449: chos kyi dbyings bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ngang du sangs rgya ba yin te /
NK110(we)003:3450: de yang rnal 'byor pa rang gi mig gi dbang po yis mthong ba'i spyod yul du /
NK110(we)003:3451: phyi rol gyi 'byung ba sa dang me dang chu
NK110(we)003:3452: dang rlung gi rnam pa rnams mi snang bar rang
NK110(we)003:3453: 'od kyi snang bar skabs su snang zhing /
NK110(we)003:3454: skabs su 'byung ba bzhi'i snang ba sus kyang byas pa med par rang nub ste /
NK110(we)003:3455: de nas thog ma'i mthing ka dang /
NK110(we)003:3457: de nas ser po dang gsum du 'gyur /
NK110(we)003:3459: de nas ljang gu'i snang ba rnams rims kyis shar nas /
NK110(we)003:3460: de ltar gong nas gong du 'phel nas /
NK110(we)003:3461: kha dog lnga la spyod pa'i tshe /
NK110(we)003:3463: 'od kyi snang ba 'di dang yo gi de 'bral ba med pa'i rtags su /
NK110(we)003:3464: 'gro ba gzhan gyis mthong ba'i mig gi spyod yul du 'khrul pa zhig pa'i skal ldan de /
NK110(we)003:3465: smyon pa bzhin du mthong ste /
NK110(we)003:3466: de nyid kyang snang ba gang la yang thogs rdugs
NK110(we)003:3467: med par mdor na 'byung ba bzhi'i gnod pa dang
NK110(we)003:3468: bral nas / chu la bying ba med pa la sogs pa yang 'byung /
NK110(we)003:3469: de dag la rang gis spyod cing gnod pa dang bral ba'o //
NK110(we)003:3470: de'i dus na skyes bu de dngos po'i rdzas gang la yang chags pa med pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3471: 'di ltar byung ba'i dus na 'byung ba bzhi'i bcings pa'i dri ma las grol ba'i rtags su /
NK110(we)003:3472: ri dang brag la sogs pa rnams la lus zang thal du 'gro bar nus pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3473: de bzhin du sa'i gting du 'dzul bar 'gro ba
NK110(we)003:3474: gzhan gyi snang ba la mthong ba dag 'byung la
NK110(we)003:3475: / de ltar chu rnams la yang bying ba med par zang thal ba'o //
NK110(we)003:3476: 'di'i dus na lus la gos dang bral nas chos
NK110(we)003:3477: kyi rang drod phebs pas kyang grang ba med pa
NK110(we)003:3478: ni / gcer bu snang ba gang la yang thogs pa med cing rgyu bar byed la /
NK110(we)003:3479: 'di'i dus na ting nge 'dzin ro mnyam gyi zas
NK110(we)003:3480: rnyed pas 'jig rten gyi khams kyi zas dang skom
NK110(we)003:3481: dang na tsha dang skye shi la sogs pa'i 'dod
NK110(we)003:3482: pa rang bzhin gyis bral bas 'dis ni snang ba
NK110(we)003:3483: 'di nyid la / zag pa dang bcas pa phung
NK110(we)003:3484: po'i zag pa dang nyon mongs pa'i zag pa rang
NK110(we)003:3485: zad nas 'byung ba bzhi rang sar dengs nas ni
NK110(we)003:3486: 'di nyid la / / zag bcas kyi phung po
NK110(we)003:3487: mi snang bar tshe 'di la sangs rgyas kyi 'bras
NK110(we)003:3488: bu thob pa la the tshom med do zhes 'od
NK110(we)003:3489: la goms pa'i rtags bstan nas /
NK110(we)003:3490: da ni dbyings la goms pa'i rtags bstan pa ni /
NK110(we)003:3491: gang gis dbyings la goms pas ni /
NK110(we)003:3492: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK110(we)003:3493: rnal 'byor pa gang zhig gis chos kyi dbyings pa ni /
NK110(we)003:3499: dbyings kyi ngo bo ni yangs shing khyab brdal chen po'i bdag nyid gsal ba rang gsal nyid do //
NK110(we)003:3500: nges tshig ni dkyil zhes bya /
NK110(we)003:3502: chos nyid dngos po gshis kyi rang bzhin yangs shing mtha' la thug pa med pa nyid do //
NK110(we)003:3505: nang gi dbyings kyi sgron ma dang /
NK110(we)003:3506: gsang ba'i dbyings 'od dang thig le dang /
NK110(we)003:3507: gsang ba bla na med pa'i dbyings 'khrul snang rang 'gags pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3508: de yang phyi'i dbyings rig pa'i yul yin /
NK110(we)003:3509: nang gi dbyings ye shes kyi yul yin /
NK110(we)003:3510: gsang ba'i dbyings sku gsum gyi yul yin /
NK110(we)003:3511: gsang ba bla na med pa'i dbyings mthar thug 'bras bu'i yul yin no //
NK110(we)003:3513: spyi mtshan dang rang mtshan las /
NK110(we)003:3514: spyi mtshan ni snang ba nus pa la khyab pa phyogs med du shar shing /
NK110(we)003:3515: gsal ba'i yul de dper na me long gi nang du bzhin snang gsal bar byed pa dang 'dra'o //
NK110(we)003:3516: mdor na chos nyid rang ni ma yin chos nyid
NK110(we)003:3517: snang bar byed pa'i yul gsal ba'i nus pa 'byin
NK110(we)003:3518: par byed pa'o // rang mtshan ni phyi'i dbyings kyi
NK110(we)003:3519: mtshan nyid stong pa ngos gzung dang bral ba yin
NK110(we)003:3520: par byed pa'o // la / nang gi gsal ba ngos bzung dang bral ba yin /
NK110(we)003:3521: gsang ba'i snang ba ngos bzung dang bral ba yin la /
NK110(we)003:3522: gsang ba bla na med pa dbyings kyi mtshan nyid myong ba ngos bzung dang bral ba'o //
NK110(we)003:3523: 'bras bu ni chos nyid kyi yul phyin ci ma
NK110(we)003:3524: log par khong du chud cing shes pa la brten
NK110(we)003:3525: nas chos nyid rang gi ngo bo phyin ci ma
NK110(we)003:3527: mngon sum mi 'gyur ba la lam du byas nas
NK110(we)003:3528: 'bras bu phyin ci ma log par sangs rgyas so
NK110(we)003:3529: // de lta bu'i dbyings la goms pa'i skal ldan de la ni /
NK110(we)003:3530: rnam par rtog pa'i rlung brgyad dang bral ba'i rtags su /
NK110(we)003:3531: dbugs ni phyir rgyu ba med par rnam par snang ba'i yul gyi rnam par rtog pa dang bral /
NK110(we)003:3532: nang du rgyu ba rang zad pa ni nang sems
NK110(we)003:3533: kyi rnam par rtog pa med pa'i rtags yin no
NK110(we)003:3534: // de ltar phyi nang gnyis kyi rnam rtog med
NK110(we)003:3535: pas lus kyi rdos pa med cing stong pa'i rtags
NK110(we)003:3536: su lus kyi phra rags nub pa ni /
NK110(we)003:3537: sngon du phyii'i dbyings la goms par byas pas de nyid la tshad 'byongs pas /
NK110(we)003:3538: lus kyi stobs kyis phyi'i nam mkha' la bya bzhin du 'gro ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3539: de bzhin du chu la yang nya bzhin du rkyal ba dang ldan pa 'dis 'gro ste /
NK110(we)003:3540: de ni phyi'i dbyings la goms pa'i rtags yin no //
NK110(we)003:3541: yang skal ldan des nang dbyings la goms pa'i rtags ni /
NK110(we)003:3542: sngar mthong ma myong ba'i yul rgya dkar po'i rgyal khams dang /
NK110(we)003:3546: de las rgya che ba'i gling bzhi ri rab dang bcas pa /
NK110(we)003:3547: yang 'dug sa gcig tu skyil krung ngam /
NK110(we)003:3551: ji ltar 'jug pa de'i lus ma zhig pa'i sgo
NK110(we)003:3552: nas mthong ba de ni ye shes kyi mig mnga'
NK110(we)003:3553: ba yin no // yang skal ldan des de dag
NK110(we)003:3554: 'das pa'i 'og tu gsang ba'i dbyings la goms pa'i
NK110(we)003:3555: rtags su chos kyi dbyings de bzhin nyid khong du
NK110(we)003:3556: chud pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sprul pa'i sku'i zhing khams
NK110(we)003:3557: ba yin no // / shar phyogs na mngon par dga' ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3558: lho phyogs na dpal dang ldan pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3559: nub phyogs na pad+ma rtsegs pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3560: byang phyogs na las rab rdzogs pa la sogs pa
NK110(we)003:3561: de dag gi yon tan rnams shes shing khong du
NK110(we)003:3562: chud pa dang / de bzhin du longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i zhing khams dum bu ba ste /
NK110(we)003:3563: rnam par snang mdzad kyi zhing khams 'khor dang gtso bo la sogs pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3564: de bzhin mi bskyod pa la sogs pa rigs lnga'i gtso 'khor gyi khyad par mthong ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3565: longs sku'i zhing khams rgya chen po phyogs bcu'i zhing khams dpag tu med pa mthong ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3566: gzhan yang chos kyi sku'i zhing khams ni grangs can dang /
NK110(we)003:3571: sngar mthong ba dag ga la srid de thos pa yang med pa rnams /
NK110(we)003:3572: da lta'i 'dug sa gcig nas zhing khams 'di kun
NK110(we)003:3573: dus gcig la skad cig ma bcu drug gi khongs
NK110(we)003:3575: ye shes chen po'i mig rnyed pas te 'di ltar
NK110(we)003:3576: rtags de dag dang 'das pa'i 'og tu skal ba
NK110(we)003:3577: dang ldan pa'i skyes bu la /
NK110(we)003:3578: gsang ba bla na med pa'i dbyings la goms pa'i rtags bstan pa ni /
NK110(we)003:3579: rtags 'di dag rnams rdzogs nas zla ba bcu drug na /
NK110(we)003:3580: chos kyi dbyings bsam gyis mi khyab pa nyid kyang skal ldan des mthong bar 'gyur te /
NK110(we)003:3581: 'di mthong ma thag tu skal ba dang ldan pa de /
NK110(we)003:3582: sku gsum gyi sangs rgyas kyi 'bras bu 'di nyid
NK110(we)003:3583: la thob par 'gyur ba la the tshom byar med
NK110(we)003:3584: do // de ltar rtags dang ldan pa 'di'i dus
NK110(we)003:3585: na skal ldan de la sdig pa mi dge ba'i
NK110(we)003:3587: gal te byung yang skal ldan de la phan pa nyams kyi grogs dang /
NK110(we)003:3588: gnod pa bsad gcod kyi rnam pa ci byas kyang rnam smin dang bral te /
NK110(we)003:3589: ye shes rang gi ngo bo la gnas pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3590: de lta bu'i rtags dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pa 'di yang snang ba 'di nyid la /
NK110(we)003:3591: 'byung ba'i zag pa dang nyon mongs pa'i dang /
NK110(we)003:3592: phung po'i zag pa phra rags bdag tu med pas gzugs phra rags kyi zag pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3593: byung tshor gang du yang ma grub /
NK110(we)003:3594: tshor ba bde sdug du ma grub pas tshor ba'i zag pa med /
NK110(we)003:3595: 'tshogs pa du mar med pas 'du shes kyi zag pa med /
NK110(we)003:3596: yul dang shes pa ci'i ngo bor yang med pas rnam par shes pa'i zag pa med /
NK110(we)003:3597: mi rtag pa ma yin te rang snang rtag pa
NK110(we)003:3598: chen por yod pas 'du byed kyi zag pa med
NK110(we)003:3599: / zag pa dang bcas pa'i phung po ni lnga ste /
NK110(we)003:3600: 'byung ba phra rags kyi tshogs pa 'dus pas gzugs kyi phung po dang /
NK110(we)003:3601: rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad yul dang yul can
NK110(we)003:3602: tha dad par snang bas rnam par shes pa'i phung
NK110(we)003:3603: po dang / tshogs pa'i chos rten 'brel dang /
NK110(we)003:3604: 'byung ba so so'i smin pa'i las dang /
NK110(we)003:3610: gdon la sogs pa so so'i rten du ma byed pas 'du byed kyi phung po dang /
NK110(we)003:3613: btang snyoms gsum 'dus pa las tshor ba'i phung po dang /
NK110(we)003:3614: phra ba'i nyon mongs pa lnga bcu rtsa lnga'i 'tshogs
NK110(we)003:3615: pa'i rten dang 'brel ba 'dus pas 'du byed kyi
NK110(we)003:3617: phung lnga mi snang bar rang sar dengs pa ni /
NK110(we)003:3618: 'byung ba bzhi sa dang chu dang me dang rlung rang gi sar rang sar dengs nas /
NK110(we)003:3619: phyi'i 'byung ba lnga'i snang ba mi snang /
NK110(we)003:3620: nang phung po lnga'i snang ba mi snang /
NK110(we)003:3621: gsang ba ye shes lnga'i snang ba tsam du yang mi snang bas /
NK110(we)003:3622: 'bras bu nges par thob par yin no //
NK110(we)003:3623: de dag ni phyi'i rtags de rang gzhan gyis tshor bar skye ba yin no //
NK110(we)003:3624: 'dir ma bstan pa'i tshig gi lhag ma nang gi nyams dang rtags ni /
NK110(we)003:3625: rgyud 'dir ni nga ston pa rdo rje 'chang gis ma bshad de /
NK110(we)003:3626: don gyi skal ldan rang gi nyams las ma skyes pas na /
NK110(we)003:3627: nyams skyes pa'i rtags de shes par 'dod na 'di
NK110(we)003:3628: ltar mkha' 'gro ma'i mdzod nas bshad pas shes par
NK110(we)003:3629: bya'o // nang gi rtags ni 'di bzhin du rig par bya'o //
NK110(we)003:3630: 'khrul pa rang gis rang gzings pa 'gyur ba'i rtags dang /
NK110(we)003:3631: man ngag gi gnad thog du ma phebs pas nges pa med pa'i rtags dang /
NK110(we)003:3632: rig pa mngon gsum gyi gnad kyis ma zin pa bar chod bdud gyi rtags dang /
NK110(we)003:3633: mngon gsum rang thog tu phebs pas 'gyur ba med cing mi 'gyur ba'i rtags dang bzhi'o //
NK110(we)003:3634: 'gyur ba'i rtags ni nyams su ma blangs pa rnams la yang 'byung ba yod kyang don mi 'byung /
NK110(we)003:3635: bya dang ri dwags la sogs pa rnams la yang
NK110(we)003:3636: 'byung ba yod de 'di ni rgyu'i rtags zhes bya
NK110(we)003:3637: ste don mi 'byung nges pa yin no //
NK110(we)003:3638: de yang nges pa med pa'i rtags ni /
NK110(we)003:3639: yid dpyod tshig la mkhas pa rang rdol ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3640: pha rol gyi shes pa dum bu pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3642: lus la sku gdung 'brul ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3643: ngag la nus pa 'byung ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3644: gzhan gyis lung ston pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3646: zhi gnas rgyun ring ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3647: lus kyi drod dum bu ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3648: 'jig rten 'dre'i cha byad mthong ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3649: chos rtsom zhing tshig gi sgro 'dogs pa rnams la bzo ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3650: shes pa'i sna dpag tu med pa 'phro ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3653: sngon bas bde ba lhag tu che ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3655: dga' ba khyad par can dang /
NK110(we)003:3657: rtag tu kha glu len snying 'dod pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3659: mig 'gro ba gzhan la mi chags pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3661: sems phyam brdal du song ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3662: shes pa rtag tu 'gyur ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3663: blo gcig tu mi phebs pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3664: tshig rnams la rtog pa 'dzud par byed pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3665: mkha' 'gro ma'i skad thos pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3666: yul mtha' 'khob kyi skye bo dang lhan cig gnas pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3668: lus kyi ba spu rnams gyen la langs pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3669: sen mo'i dkyil na yi ge rnams rang byung ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3670: rgang nas so'u skye ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3671: gzhan gyi lus la byin brlabs bstim pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3672: skyil krung nam mkha' la 'phar ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3673: lag pa'i mthil na tsakra yod pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3674: rkang pa'i sor mo gnyis 'brel ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3677: lus byol song du sprul shes pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3678: yan lag la ring bsrel phra mo dag 'brul ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3679: lha dang lha min brtsod pa mthong ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3680: yi ge 'bru sbyor la mkhas pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3682: mi ma yin rnams dang gleng bar nus pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3684: nyi zla 'dzin par nus pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3685: gzhan gyi 'byung ba 'khrugs pa'i 'du shes pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3686: lus la me stag 'phro ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3687: thal mo brdab pa la sgra ngo mtshar can 'byung
NK110(we)003:3688: ba dang lnga bcu tham pa ni lus ngag sems
NK110(we)003:3689: la mngon par 'byung ba'i nges pa med pa'i rtags
NK110(we)003:3690: so // 'di ltar rmi lam gyis 'gyur zhing nges pa med pa'i rtags ni /
NK110(we)003:3691: rtag tu chos smra ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3701: seng ge'i khri la 'dug pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3702: yul nges pa sna tshogs pa mthong ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3704: rang rgyal dang byang chub sems dpa' mthong ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3705: shel gyi mchod rten la 'dzeg pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3706: gser gyi skas la 'dzeg pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3707: gangs kyi stangs na bsgom pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3708: nam mkha' la 'phur zhing sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams mthong ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3709: seng ge la zhon nas phyogs bcur 'gro ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3710: shes kyi mdung ring gzhan la brdeg pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3711: sems can rnams ngan song nas bton pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3712: 'khor ba'i chu bo las brgal ba rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3713: lus barjesa par rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3714: ston pa'i zhal mthong ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3715: rin po che'i gter rnyed pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3716: 'gro ba drug skyabs gnas su btsud pa rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3718: bla ma dang mkhan pos lung bstan pa rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3720: chos thams cad shes par rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3721: dbus kyi ri bo'i rtser phyin pa rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3722: ngan song gsum rgyun chad par gyur cig ces smon lam 'debs pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3723: bdag nyid sangs rgyas par rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3724: 'gro ba drug gi kha lo gyen la bsgyur ba rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3725: yan lag rnams rin po che'i mchod rten du song bar rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3726: bdag gi lus la sangs rgyas kyi sprul pa 'gyed cing rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3727: khams gsum dong nas bton par rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3728: gser gyi mda' gzhu 'dzin par rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3729: mgo bo'i steng du sangs rgyas bzhugs pa rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3730: bdag nyid kyi lus zang thal du song ba rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3731: 'khor ba rgyun chad par rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3732: bdag nyid la rgyal pos dbang bskur bar rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3733: bdud rnams pham par byas par rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3734: rang gis lus rang gis sbyangs par rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3735: skye rga na 'chi'i chu bo bzhi'i rgyun chad do zhes sgra thos pa rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3736: bdag nyid byang chub sems dpa'i lus su sprul bar rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3737: chos nyid brjod du med pa'i don rtogs par rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3738: bdag nyid lus mi 'dra ba dag tu sprul bar rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3739: ngag gis 'gro ba rnams bsdus par rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3740: sems kyi mtshan nyid mthong bar rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3741: lha rnams kyi yul mthong bar rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3742: gser gyi lha khang gi yang thog na 'dug par rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3743: sangs rgyas kyi gsung thos pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3745: thugs kyi dgongs pa rtogs par nus pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3746: lag pas gser gyi gdugs gnyis bzung nas nam mkha' la 'phur ba rmis pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3747: lha dang lha min gyis phyag byed par rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3748: yid bzhin gyi nor bu'i phung po la spyod par rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3749: gser gyi glegs bam gyi char babs pa rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3750: chos kyi sgra sna tshogs pa bdag nyid kyi rna bar grags pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3751: bdag nyid la sil snyan sna tshogs pas mchod par rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3752: lha'i dbang pos rin po che'i khri rkang pa bzhi
NK110(we)003:3753: dang ldan pa'i steng du bzhag nas nam mkha' la
NK110(we)003:3754: bteg nas 'gro ba rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3755: klu'i rgyal po rnams kyis bdag la nor bu rin po che ster ba rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3756: bar ma do'i snang ba 'char ba rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3757: glang po che zhon nas skyes bu stobs dang ldan
NK110(we)003:3758: pa bzhis rkang pa bzhi nas bteg nas nam mkha'i
NK110(we)003:3759: mthong na yar 'gro ba rmi ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3760: gser gyi 'khor lo'i steng na bdag nyid gnas nas
NK110(we)003:3761: nam mkha' la lan gsum 'phar bar rmi ba dang
NK110(we)003:3762: / drug bcu rtsa drug ste brgya dang bcu drug ni nges pa med pa'i rtags so //
NK110(we)003:3763: de rnams ni lam gyi rtags te /
NK110(we)003:3765: bar chad kyi rtags ni lus sna tshogs su sprul shes pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3767: gang du phyin pa'i sa phyogs su sgra 'byung ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3768: gzhan la nus pa 'jug pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3770: tshig gi sgros 'dogs pa la bzo ba rnams ni
NK110(we)003:3771: gang zag de la bar chod byung ba'i rtags so
NK110(we)003:3772: // de ltar rtags gsum po de su la byung kyang gnad kyi man ngag 'di ltar byas te /
NK110(we)003:3773: 'gyur ba'i rtags byung ba la skabs su chu dkyil du sdad cing /
NK110(we)003:3774: 'jing pa gnyis shing gi byang bu sor bcu drug pa'i nang du stems te /
NK110(we)003:3775: lus la tsan dan gyi mar gyis rtag tu byugs nas /
NK110(we)003:3776: phyi nang thams cad dngos po rags par bsgoms nas
NK110(we)003:3777: 'bras bu thams cad chud mi zos pa yin no
NK110(we)003:3778: // nges pa med pa'i rtags byung ba la ni /
NK110(we)003:3779: lus la bsil ba'i gos gyon cing kha zas kyang bsil ba bza'/
NK110(we)003:3780: ngag tu a'i rnam pa bzlas shing /
NK110(we)003:3781: sems kyis nam mkha' la sangs rgyas kyi sku mang po bsgom pas /
NK110(we)003:3782: phar cher nges pa can gyi rtags su 'gro ba yin no //
NK110(we)003:3784: lus sna tshogs su sprul pa 'di yang bdud kyis byin gyis brlabs pa yin te /
NK110(we)003:3785: de nyid la rab tu brtags na gzugs brnyan gnyis par snang bar yin no //
NK110(we)003:3786: de ltar ma mthong na de nyid la gu gul nag po dang /
NK110(we)003:3787: nim pa'i chus lus mgo 'jug tu byug cing /
NK110(we)003:3788: yan lag lnga la sder so rnying pa'i sa 'dags gis byugs na /
NK110(we)003:3790: de ltar byung na de'i lus la de bzhin gshegs
NK110(we)003:3791: pa'i sku gzugs mi long la bstan pa de'i khrus
NK110(we)003:3792: chab kyis bkrus pa'i khrus chab kyis bkru /
NK110(we)003:3793: ngag tu phata kyi rnam pa bzlas shing /
NK110(we)003:3794: sems kyis phyi nang thams cad stong pa nyid du bsgoms pas bar chod zhi ba yin no //
NK110(we)003:3798: tshig la sogs pa rnams la yang bya'o //
NK110(we)003:3799: de ltar bar chod kyi rtags byung ba la man
NK110(we)003:3800: ngag de lta bu dang mi ldan na yi dwags
NK110(we)003:3801: kyi skye gnas su skye ba yin no //
NK110(we)003:3802: de dag ni theg pa thun mong ba rnams kyi 'gyur ba'i rtags yin no //
NK110(we)003:3803: rig pa mngon gsum gyi don mthong ba rnams la ni /
NK110(we)003:3805: de yang dngos po mthong ba'i gnad kyis byas pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3806: 'di nyid kyi rtags ni gsum ste /
NK110(we)003:3807: rang gis mthong la gzhan gyis mi mthong ba'i rtags dang /
NK110(we)003:3808: gzhan gyis mthong la rang gis mi mthong ba'i rtags dang /
NK110(we)003:3809: rang gzhan gnyis ka'i rtags rnams te /
NK110(we)003:3810: 'di dag ni rtags kyi yi ge dang sbyar 'og nas kyang ston to //
NK110(we)003:3811: de lta bu'i rtags gsum dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor
NK110(we)003:3812: pa des lus ngag rnal du phebs pa yin pas
NK110(we)003:3813: / rtags 'di ltar byung ba'i gang zag gis rtags 'di kun so so'i skye bo dang /
NK110(we)003:3814: nyan thos dang dam tshig mi gcig pa rnams la rab tu gsang ngo //
NK110(we)003:3815: de nyid gsang ba'i rtags 'di nyid kyi yon tan
NK110(we)003:3816: rnal 'byor pa de'i lus ngag sems la ldan pa
NK110(we)003:3817: ste / de ltar yon tan rdzogs pa'i dus na /
NK110(we)003:3818: dag pa'i snang ba rang shar ba ni ye shes lnga'i rang rtags so //
NK110(we)003:3819: zhes dbyings la goms pa'i rtags bstan nas /
NK110(we)003:3820: da ni thig le la goms pa'i skal ldan la rtags ji ltar 'byung ba bstan pa ni /
NK110(we)003:3821: thig le klong du sus gyur ba //
NK110(we)003:3822: zhes pa sogs pas bstan te /
NK110(we)003:3823: thig le ni ngo bo dang /
NK110(we)003:3828: thig le'i ngo bo tha dad pa ma yin par
NK110(we)003:3829: gcig tu gnas pa yin cing zla dang bral ba'o
NK110(we)003:3830: // nges tshig ni thig mi 'gyur cing drang por gnas pa'am cha mtshon par byed pa yin la /
NK110(we)003:3831: le brdal ba chen po thams cad la ma khyab pa med pa la bya'o //
NK110(we)003:3832: dbye na lus gnas gzhi'i thig le dang /
NK110(we)003:3833: rang bzhin lam gyi thig le dang /
NK110(we)003:3834: mthar phyin 'bras bu'i thig le dang gsum mo //
NK110(we)003:3836: kun rdzob rgyu'i thig le dang /
NK110(we)003:3837: don dam ye shes kyi thig le'o //
NK110(we)003:3838: kun rdzob kyi thig le ni /
NK110(we)003:3839: 'byung ba bzhi'i dngas ma 'dus pa pha ma'i byang chub sems kyi thig le de /
NK110(we)003:3840: kun rdzob bskyed par byed pa'i rgyu 'byung ba bzhi'i bdag nyid can no //
NK110(we)003:3841: de la brten nas lus bskyed pa ste /
NK110(we)003:3842: thig le de la 'byung ba me'i dwangs ma yod pas dro bas drod du bskyed la /
NK110(we)003:3843: sa'i dwangs ma yod pas sra ba sa des sha bskyed /
NK110(we)003:3844: chu'i dngas ma yod pas sdud pa chus te khrag bskyed /
NK110(we)003:3845: rlung gi dwangs ma yod pas yang ba rlung ste
NK110(we)003:3846: dbugs bskyed pas lus zhes bya ba grub pas na
NK110(we)003:3847: kun rdzob bo // don dam ye shes kyi thig le lnga ste /
NK110(we)003:3848: gzhi'i thig le bzang po 'od kyi gong bur de
NK110(we)003:3849: ltar lus su grub pa rtsa'i nang na gnas shing
NK110(we)003:3850: g.yo 'gul med / lam gyi thig le bzang po
NK110(we)003:3851: rtsa'i nang nas ye shes kyi rlung gis bskyod nas
NK110(we)003:3852: g.yo 'gul med / 'gro 'ong byed / bzang po'i bzang po sgron ma yul la 'char bar byed /
NK110(we)003:3853: bzang po'i rtse mo shes rab kyi gcod sna tshogs par rtsa'i nang nas bskyod par byed /
NK110(we)003:3854: bzang po rgyan dang ldan pa'i thig le ni sgron
NK110(we)003:3855: ma rnam pa bzhi la brten nas nyams gong nas
NK110(we)003:3856: gong du 'phel bar byed pa'i snang ba ston par
NK110(we)003:3857: byed pa'o // rang bzhin lam gyi thig le ni /
NK110(we)003:3858: chos nyid kyi thig le bcos pa med cing kun la khyab pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3859: kun tu bzang po bzang ngan dang che chung med par snang ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3860: dbyings kyi thig le phyi nang med par gsal ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3861: dbyings rnam par dag pa'i thig le gol sgrib dang phyogs lhung med par rang shar ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3862: ye shes kyi thig le ye nas byas pa med par rang bzhugs pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3863: ye shes chen po'i thig le nyon mongs pa gang
NK110(we)003:3864: gis kyang ma sgrib par mngon gsum du snang ba
NK110(we)003:3865: dang drug go // mthar phyin pa 'bras bu'i thig
NK110(we)003:3866: le ni chos kyi sku'i thig le nyag gcig spros
NK110(we)003:3867: pa gang gis kyang ma spros /
NK110(we)003:3868: bsdus pa sus kyang ma bsdus /
NK110(we)003:3869: 'di 'dra zhes mtshan nyid dang bral la /
NK110(we)003:3870: ngo bo ngos bzung dang bral la /
NK110(we)003:3871: rtsal sna tshogs su snang la /
NK110(we)003:3872: grub rgyu gang du yang med pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3874: gnod 'jug zug rngu dang bral ba'o //
NK110(we)003:3875: zlum po spros pa med la /
NK110(we)003:3876: rig pa mtshon pa'i rnam pa dum bur bstan pas ye shes zang thal du yod la /
NK110(we)003:3877: mu 'khyud lnga gcig tu zlums pas sku'i gnas yin la /
NK110(we)003:3878: stong nyid rdzas su ma grub pas ngos bzung las 'das pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3879: de las snang ba'i 'phel rnams 'byung bas yon tan
NK110(we)003:3880: phyogs med du shar skyon gang gis kyang ma gos
NK110(we)003:3881: pas / mtshan nyid la dri ma med /
NK110(we)003:3882: rtsal 'gag pa med pas rol pa sna tshogs su shar /
NK110(we)003:3883: mtshan nyid gnyis su med pas ngo bo rang dag la /
NK110(we)003:3884: gtan tshigs phyogs med du shar bas gnas lugs su rang grol ba'o //
NK110(we)003:3885: 'bras bu ni thig le la rang bzhin phyi nang med pas snang srid zang thal du grol /
NK110(we)003:3886: mtshan nyid ngos bzung med pas snang ba phyogs med du grol /
NK110(we)003:3887: gtan tshigs la 'gyur ldog med pas /
NK110(we)003:3888: dam bca' la yin min med par grol ba'o //
NK110(we)003:3889: de lta bu'i thig le de klong du skal ba ldan pa sus mngon du gyur pa 'di ni /
NK110(we)003:3890: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i skal ba yod pas
NK110(we)003:3891: chos nyid stong pa nyid kyi don dang ldan pa
NK110(we)003:3892: de chos kyi sku'i thig le nyag gcig mthong ba'i
NK110(we)003:3893: rtags ni / rang gi mig nas thig le stong pa'i sgron ma ni /
NK110(we)003:3894: rang gi mtheb mdzub kyis rtsol ba med par nam
NK110(we)003:3895: mkha' stong pa la rang shar ba ni de nyid
NK110(we)003:3896: tshe'i dus byas kyang mngal gyi sgor mi 'jug nges
NK110(we)003:3898: yang skal ldan de la 'di kun rang gis nyams su blangs pa'i rtags ni /
NK110(we)003:3899: tshig gi spros pa med pa la yod par sgro btags dang /
NK110(we)003:3900: yod pa la med par dang /
NK110(we)003:3901: yin pa la min par dang /
NK110(we)003:3902: min pa la yin par tshig gis sgro btags dang /
NK110(we)003:3903: yid kyis dpyad cing gcig las tha dad du spros pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3904: don gcig la tshig gis don tha dad du ngos bzung ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3905: ngo bo gtan la ma phebs par mtshan nyid 'tshol ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3906: don mtshon pa'i tshig gcig gis chog pa yin pa la /
NK110(we)003:3907: de las spros pas don ma rnyed pa rnams kyis
NK110(we)003:3908: spros pa ma chod de tshig gang yang btags shing
NK110(we)003:3909: dpyad pa med pa rnams ni skyon can dang yang
NK110(we)003:3910: dag pa ni / grub mtha' gzhan gyis tshig zab
NK110(we)003:3911: mo la blo skad cig kyang 'jug par mi 'gyur
NK110(we)003:3912: dag pa ni / te / tshig gi spros pa la rtog pa'i skabs med par gnas pa ni /
NK110(we)003:3913: gnas lugs kyi don 'ba' zhig la gnas pa'i rtags yin te /
NK110(we)003:3914: de nyid kyi lus su rnal 'byor pa rang gis
NK110(we)003:3915: smra bar byed pa'i gtam rgyun chad pa ni tshig
NK110(we)003:3916: gi brjod pa zad pa'i phyir ro //
NK110(we)003:3917: 'di'i dus na rnal 'byor pa 'di yang lkug pa
NK110(we)003:3918: lta bur gyur te 'gro ba gzhan la smra bar
NK110(we)003:3919: byed pa dag ga la srid de smra'o snyam pa'i
NK110(we)003:3920: bsam pa yang / skyes bu 'di la 'byung mi
NK110(we)003:3921: srid pa ni chos nyid brjod du med pa'i don
NK110(we)003:3922: khong du chud pa'i rtags yin /
NK110(we)003:3923: de nyid gzhan gyi sgra nyan pa dang tshig nyan
NK110(we)003:3924: pa'i rjes su sems pa dag ga la 'gyur te
NK110(we)003:3925: / 'di ltar gang zag su la snang ba shar ba de /
NK110(we)003:3926: dngos po gshis kyi 'dug tshul spros pa med pa'i
NK110(we)003:3927: chos kyi sku'i thig le nyag gcig skyes bu des
NK110(we)003:3928: rtsad nas chod pa yin pas /
NK110(we)003:3929: de'i phyir na 'di ltar rtags dang ldan pa de ni /
NK110(we)003:3930: sku gsum gyi snang ba'i rtags te /
NK110(we)003:3931: de nas lo ni gnyis na yang dag pa'i ye
NK110(we)003:3932: shes rang gi rig pa nyid kyis snang ba tshad
NK110(we)003:3934: de nas dbyings phyi nang 'dres pa rang rig pa'i rang snang gnyis /
NK110(we)003:3936: de ltar rig pa tshad la phebs pa'i snang ba dang /
NK110(we)003:3937: dus thams cad du 'bral ba med pa de'i ngang la skal ldan de 'dug pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3938: de nas chos rnams rang zad pas gang zag de
NK110(we)003:3939: yang lus kyi 'byung bzhi rang dengs su 'gyur bar
NK110(we)003:3940: tshe 'di la the tshom med do //
NK110(we)003:3941: zhes thig le la goms pa'i rtags 'bras bu dang bcas pa bstan nas /
NK110(we)003:3942: da ni sku la goms pa'i rtags la bye brag
NK110(we)003:3943: tu chos kyi sku la goms pa'i rtags bstan pa
NK110(we)003:3944: ni / gang gis sku la tshad 'byongs pa //
NK110(we)003:3945: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK110(we)003:3946: rnal 'byor pa gang zhig gis spyir sku thams cad
NK110(we)003:3947: la bye brag tu sku gsum la tshad 'byongs pa
NK110(we)003:3948: ni / rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i skal pa dang ldan pa'i skyes bu la /
NK110(we)003:3949: phyi rol mngon pa'i yul du rtags ni 'di lta bu 'byung ba yin te /
NK110(we)003:3950: de yang bye brag tu chos kyi sku la 'byongs pa'i rtags ni /
NK110(we)003:3957: chos kyi sku'i ngo bo ni yul du med la stong pa nyid gzugs can ma yin la /
NK110(we)003:3959: dus thams cad pa'i ye shes tshad dang ldan pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3960: nges tshig ni chos nyid phyin ci ma log pa
NK110(we)003:3961: thams cad 'dus pa'i sku gang gis kyang mi shigs
NK110(we)003:3962: pas na lam gyi mthar thug ste /
NK110(we)003:3963: chos mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos /
NK110(we)003:3964: sku skye 'jig med pas chos kyi sku zhes bya'o //
NK110(we)003:3965: dbye na 'khor ba'i chos sku dang /
NK110(we)003:3966: mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos sku'o //
NK110(we)003:3970: byang chub sems dpa'i chos sku ste /
NK110(we)003:3971: nyan thos kyi chos sku dgra bcom pa /
NK110(we)003:3972: rang rgyal rang sangs rgyas nyid /
NK110(we)003:3973: byang chub sems dpa'i chos sku bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa'o //
NK110(we)003:3974: mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos sku ni gsum ste /
NK110(we)003:3975: chos kyi sku'i sprul pa'i sku /
NK110(we)003:3976: sngags phyi'i mthar thug gi 'bras bu /
NK110(we)003:3977: chos kyi sku'i longs sku sngags nang pa'i mthar thug gi 'bras bu'o //
NK110(we)003:3978: chos kyi sku'i chos sku rdzogs pa chen po kha cig gi 'bras bu'o //
NK110(we)003:3979: mtshan nyid ni nyan thos kyi chos kyi mtshan nyid /
NK110(we)003:3980: phyi gzung ba'i yul gyi dgra bcom pas chos kyi bdag med pa la /
NK110(we)003:3981: nang 'dzin pa'i sems kyi dgra bcom pas phung po
NK110(we)003:3982: dang khams la bdag med pas chos kyi sku yin
NK110(we)003:3983: par 'dod la / rang rgyal ba'i chos kyi sku'i
NK110(we)003:3984: mtshan nyid ni rang gis rten cing 'brel pa'i chos
NK110(we)003:3986: de nyid la gnas pa'i stobs kyis chos nyid la bdag gtan med la /
NK110(we)003:3987: nang sems las byung ba'i rten cing 'brel ba lugs
NK110(we)003:3988: 'byung dang lugs bzlog tu bsgoms pas gang zag gi
NK110(we)003:3990: de nyid chos nyid rang gi ngo bo chos skur 'dod pa'o //
NK110(we)003:3991: byang sems kyi chos kyi sku ni /
NK110(we)003:3992: sems tsam pa sems las snang ba sems las byung bas chos kyi bdag med la /
NK110(we)003:3993: sems nyid phyi rol du snang bas gang zag gi bdag med /
NK110(we)003:3994: de ltar sems dang sems las byung ba thams cad rang rig rang gsal don dam du 'dod pas /
NK110(we)003:3995: de nyid phung po'i yul dang /
NK110(we)003:3996: zhen pa'i shes pa dang bral ba ni /
NK110(we)003:3997: chos kyi sku yin te bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa de nyid thob par 'dod pa dang /
NK110(we)003:3998: dbu ma pas stong pa ci'i ngo bo yang ma grub pa nyid /
NK110(we)003:3999: chos nyid spros pa dang bral ba la /
NK110(we)003:4000: kun rdzob kyi snang ba 'di la snang mi srid pas /
NK110(we)003:4001: dper na bud shing zad pas me rang shi nas
NK110(we)003:4002: rgyu rkyen skye rgyu med pa dang 'dra ba nyid
NK110(we)003:4003: chos sku zhes tha snyad du byas te /
NK110(we)003:4004: de nyid sa bcu gcig pa yin par 'dod la /
NK110(we)003:4005: pha rol du phyin pas sa bcu rim gyis bgrod
NK110(we)003:4006: pa'i tha ma bcu gcig pa la shes bya'i sgrib
NK110(we)003:4007: pa zad nas sangs rgya bar 'dod pa ni /
NK110(we)003:4008: de nyid chos kyi sku ste chos kyi mchog zhes bya'o //
NK110(we)003:4009: sngags phyi pa'i chos sku'i sprul pa sku ni /
NK110(we)003:4010: dpal rdo rje 'chang mtshan nyid mngon par byang chub pa lnga dang ldan pa'o //
NK110(we)003:4011: sngags nang pa'i chos kyi sku'i longs sku dpal kun
NK110(we)003:4012: tu bzang po rang bzhin gyi mtshan nyid gsum dang
NK110(we)003:4013: ldan pa / rdzogs pa chen po la la dag
NK110(we)003:4014: gi chos kyi sku'i chos kyi sku gzhi dngos po'i
NK110(we)003:4015: gnas lugs ma bcos lhun gyis grub pa'i mtshan nyid
NK110(we)003:4016: ldan pa / dang / ma 'gags rol par shar ba'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK110(we)003:4017: ma bsgoms rang sar grol ba'i mtshan nyid dang rnam pa gsum dang ldan pa'o //
NK110(we)003:4018: rdzogs pa chen po de'i lugs kyis ni /
NK110(we)003:4019: chos kyi sku lam gyi snang ba yin par 'dod pas te /
NK110(we)003:4020: chos ji srid yod pa'i bar la blo yod pas kyang lam yin la /
NK110(we)003:4021: sku ji srid yod kyi bar la yang lus yod
NK110(we)003:4022: pa'i phyir na 'di dag ni lam gyi snang ba
NK110(we)003:4023: yin te / mthar thug ni ma yin no //
NK110(we)003:4024: 'di'i dngos gzhi zag pa med pa'i ye shes nyams
NK110(we)003:4025: su blangs pas rig pa tshad la phebs pa'i snang
NK110(we)003:4026: ba'i dus na / chos nyid kyi mtha' zad du nye ba'i dus yin pas /
NK110(we)003:4027: 'di'i dus na chos kyi sku yin no //
NK110(we)003:4029: 'di'i lugs kyis lam gyi mthar thug yin la /
NK110(we)003:4030: gzhan dag ni sangs rgyas dngos kyi 'bras bur 'dod pa'o //
NK110(we)003:4031: de lta bu la skal ldan sus goms pa ni /
NK110(we)003:4032: 'gro ba gzhan gyis mthong ba'i spyod yul du rnal
NK110(we)003:4033: 'byor pa de'i lus ni sus kyang mi mthong bar
NK110(we)003:4034: / rnal pa lus ngag yid rnal du phab pas /
NK110(we)003:4035: dngos gzhi zag pa med pa'i ye shes la 'byor pa de nyid /
NK110(we)003:4036: rang gi snang ba la 'byung bas mi 'grib par
NK110(we)003:4037: gang dgar rol pa sna tshogs su snang bar byed
NK110(we)003:4038: pa'o // de ni chos nyid kyi don khong du chud pa'i rtags yin no //
NK110(we)003:4039: yang rnal 'byor pa gang zhig brtsol bas ma btsal bar gzhag pa'i bsam gtan ni /
NK110(we)003:4040: rnal 'byor pa rang gi rgyud la phyin ci ma log pa skyes pa'i rtags su /
NK110(we)003:4041: rnal 'byor pa de'i blo dang bcas pa'i shes pa
NK110(we)003:4042: ji mi snyam pa'i nyams ni lkug pa'i rmi lam
NK110(we)003:4043: lta bu dang / gzhon nu ma'i bde ba lta bur 'gyur ba yin no //
NK110(we)003:4044: de nyid rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa kun gyi sems la de ltar snang ba'o //
